Knowledge, Skills, and Abilities 
 
 Ability to deliver presentations to small and large scientific audiences. 
 Soft skills, with a passion for providing superior customer service 
 Basic skills in Information Technology (IT) and network knowledge 
 Ability to provide complex data in an easy to understand format 
 Critical thinking skills 
 Ability to work for extended periods of time using computer screens 
 
 
